Package: lpirfs
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Impulse Response Functions based on Local Projections by Jordà (2005)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Philipp Adämmer
Maintainer: Philipp Adämmer <adaemmer@hsu-hh.de>
Description: The package estimates linear and non-linear impulse response functions based on the local projection method by Jordà (2005).
              The non-linear irfs are based on a transition function as used in Auerbach & Gorodnichenko (2012).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
